BBQ Blitz - Season 1, Episode 4




Alabama Brawl

It's a big family reunion as Food Network Star winner Eddie Jackson heads to his hometown of Montgomery, Ala. and finds three local chefs to test their grilling skills in a barbecue throwdown. Special judges Chris Lilly, vice president of the famous Big Bob Gibson Bar-B-Q, and NFL star Eddie "Boo" Williams must determine who will be the BBQ Blitz champion and win $5,000.




Original Air Date: 29-Oct-2015
